-- Blue Financial Service Says Its Auditors Cast Doubt Over Company's Future
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-06-21T05:18:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/blue-financial-service-says-its-auditors-cast-doubt-over-company-s-future.html

          
          
             Blue Financial Services Ltd. said
its auditors Deloitte & Touche issued a disclaimer which cast
“significant doubt” over the company’s ability to continue as
a going concern.  
          
          


  


        